title: This Is What You Do If You Have No Talent
description: If you don’t think you can accomplish your dreams, watch this! . . "The separation of talent and skill is one of the greatest misunderstood concepts for people who are trying to excel, who have dreams, who want to do things. Talent you have naturally. Skill is only developed by hours and hours and hours of beating on your craft." - Will Smith "I’ve never really viewed myself as particularly talented. Where I excel is ridiculous, sickening work ethic." - Will Smith Music Sources Fearless Motivation - Reach The Top Website: http://www.fearlessmotivation.com/ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fearlessmotivationofficial Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCf9_s9ii6BZ-klpgmtIi3WQ Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/1FhamVtJlNqaekPnwxQpbk
